result.execSummary:
The defendant Kelsey Lloyd Kenney was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case.

  • 4th Degree Sexual Assault, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.225(3m).
  • Impersonating a Peace Officer to Aid in Commission of Crime, a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 946.70(1)(a).
  • Bail Jumping-Misdemeanor, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
